Definition: something that is strikingly attractive or has great popular appeal
Example: she has a show-stopper of a smile; the brilliant orange flowers against the green foliage were a showstopper
Synonyms: showstopper, attraction, something, that, is, strikingly, attractive, or, has, great, popular, appeal, she, a, of, smile, the, brilliant, orange, flowers, against, green, foliage, were
Category: noun.attribute
